# map-client Rules

- Integrate map rendering in the app layer with `react-map-gl/maplibre`.
- Keep application state in Zustand stores.
- Sync URL query state with nuqs.
- Preserve one-way flow: MapConfig -> Zod parse -> store hydration -> UI -> URL.
- Keep library components controlled from app state.

Required references:

- `.claude/skills/project-conventions/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/extend-map-config/SKILL.md`
- `.agent/workflows/development.md`
